desc_long								关于这款游戏							Ninjahtic Mind Tricks is an 8-bit hack-and-slash platformer with stealth, adventure, and puzzle elements. Like it's predecessor, Ninjahtic, levels have an open-ended nature and are presented in a linear fashion. Though, several features have been added to the predecessor's formula to create a more varied experience.Features:Various platforming challenges with a mixture of hack-and-slash, stealth, adventure, and puzzle elementsOpen ended levels requiring the use of the environment and abilities for progressionEnemies of various types8-bit graphics and soundtrackSupports Xbox 360 Controller						
